      • canSetCustomValue

        boolean canSetCustomValue(String columnUID,
                          Object value)
        Checks whether column value could be set for HM relationship. The "Custom" value means value of column that is not present on "Edit relationship dialog".
        Parameters:
        columnUID - - UID of column
        value - - value to set
        Returns:
        true if value could be set

      • getChangedColumns
